report.title: Recibo para Hicomp Computacion con Vencimientos
report.name: recibo-hicomp-venc

querysource.name: recibo-hicomp
querysource.sql: SELECT r.id_recibo AS numero, substr( '0000000000' || r.serie, -5, 5 ) || '-' || substr( '0000000000' || r.numero, -5, 5 ) AS NumSerie, strftime( '%d %m %Y', r.fecha_pago ) AS fecha, r.texto AS contenido, r.precio AS total, c.calle || ' ' || c.numero AS direccion, c.razon_social AS cliente, c.`CUIT/CUIL` AS cuit, CASE r.forma_pago WHEN 1 THEN 'X' ELSE ' ' END AS contado, CASE r.forma_pago WHEN 0 THEN 'X' ELSE ' ' END AS ctacte FROM recibos AS r, clientes AS c WHERE r.id_recibo = <? value("id_recibo") ?> AND c.id = r.id_cliente;
